description: The Lancaster Cupcake bringing joy to every cupcake fan with every delicious bite. Their determination to bring the best local ingredients from the heart of Lancaster County has put them on top of their competition. Lancaster Cupcake have been making the best since 2011, taking them to claim a spot in 101 all time best cupcakes across the nation. Next time looking to finish your day with a smile head to Lancaster Cupcake for your well deserved sweet treat!
name: Lancaster Cupcake
